OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSome firms unaware of new  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsingle-use plastic ban     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Firms have told the BBC they were not  
OL,6, aware of a ban in England on single-use
OL,7, plastic cutlery, plates and polystyrene
OL,8, trays that comes into force on Sunday. 
OL,10,FThe ban does not extend to plastic     
OL,11,Fcontainers and trays used in takeaways 
OL,12,For for pre-packaged food in shops.     
OL,14,FEnvironmental campaigners said the new 
OL,15,Frules do not go far enough, and called 
OL,16,Fthe government's approach "piecemeal". 
OL,18,FThe government said it was the "next   
OL,19,Fbig step" in its "journey to eliminate 
OL,20,Fall avoidable plastic waste by 2042".  
